'**Temperature influence:** Temperature affects the solubility of carbon dioxide in liquids.', '**Pressure effects:** Increasing pressure can enhance the dissolution of carbon dioxide.', '**Liquid composition:** Different liquids have varying capacities to hold carbon dioxide.', '**Contact time:** The duration of contact between the liquid and carbon dioxide gas influences the degree of
